pan></span></span></code> </div><div class="max-w-[75ch]"><div data-color-mode="dark" data-light-theme="light" data-dark-theme="dark" class="markdown-body"><p>Decodes <code>buf</code> to a string according to the specified character encoding in<code>encoding</code>. <code>start</code> and <code>end</code> may be passed to decode only a subset of <code>buf</code>.</p>
